            Listed in Retail Therapy


New York and Company specializes mainly in women's business attire. This location is more of an outlet, so the clothes are well-priced -- especially when you manage to walk in on a store-wide sale. Today, NY&C was on its last day of the Columbus Weekend Sale, and I made sure to take full advantage of the mark-downs.One of the best things about shopping at the Great Mall's NY&C has to be the amazing service the staff provides. While I did not manage to catch the names of the girls that assisted me, they have my eternal gratitude for helping make my day's shopping experience wonderful. The staff will ensure that your time spent in the store is pain-free. They will offer to take your items and reserve a dressing room for you. When you're trying things on in the dressing room, they frequently stop by to see if you need a different size or color. In addition to having an awesome staff, the store's layout is incredibly well organized. Clothing is easy to find, and there's always a multitude of sizes. Also, since NY&C's focus is women's business attire, you can pick up all your fashion essentials (skirt, pants, blouse, blazer, dress, etc) here. All-in-all, today's experience  has guaranteed my continued patronage.

















