        4/19/2015
    








1 check-in
        


This is definitely my go to store of choice of all of the locations near me. The store is always very well organized, lots of choices of sizes, and the staff is always extremely friendly & welcoming! You can always count on a team member being on the floor to offer assistance & offer a fitting room if needed. Line is moved quick at checkout. The only con I can say is, the fitting rooms can use a little sprucing up. They are clean, but missing a majority of the hooks to hang up your clothes or purse. Other than that, two thumbs up for sure!




