        4/2/2016
    

I love this store they always have great deals and quality clothes. I called the Pleasanton location this morning using the app on my phone looking for black sailor pants with the buttons on the front. I spoke to Victoria and I inquired about these pants she found them in my size along with a couple of sweaters that I was looking for. She told me she would put them on hold for me to pick up this afternoon. She also looked up a couple of other items I was looking for. They weren't a available, but it's cool since I can get these online. I came in as planned and Victoria had everything  ready that I wanted to purchase. I found a nice sweater for $7.00. The other lady Daysha who took over for Victoria to finish ringing me up noticed their was a red stain on it and immediately assisted me with picking a duplicate of this sweater without the stain. Great looking out because not everyone pays attention to detail when ringing up customer purchases. This sweater works well for me since I work in the city and you never know about the weather. Plus it will come in handy if the rain returns. Victoria and Daysha were very professional and helpful. I'm happy with my purchases.  I spent $48.15 saved $105.88 today. Woo who!








