        7/9/2009
    

I'm writing in regards to the location in the Sun Valley mall. I am not crazy about going to the Sun Valley mall however they do have some nice shops in there.I have been coming here for years, there clothes are not top quality though quality enough and seem to last fairly long.This particular store always seems to have a great selection of sharp, modern style chic clothes all the way from casual nice, sharp looking work wear clothes and a descent selection of going out clothes and best of all they have a petite section.Store is bright and clean. Good service are a hit and miss here like any department store. Today service was especially helpful. There is Limited amount of Fitting rooms  though they are bright and large with GOOD LIGHTING a +...lol they have a descent selection of nice sharp new edge jewelry (don't last particular long being a little cheap) shoes look a little on the cheaper side. As for everything else is stylish comfortable and seems to last pretty long depending how you care for  it.Prices can be a little expensive however they are always having a lot of great sales.




