What we doNew York ATM Services 

Nationwide ATM Company
ATM Sales, ATM Service, ATM Leasing, ATM Processing
Best Products is a Nationwide ATM Company. We specialize in ATM sales, ATM service, ATM leasing and ATM processing across the country. We represent all the major retail ATM manufacturers such as Nautilus Hyosung ATMs, Genmega ATMs, Hantle ATMs and Triton ATMs. Our customer base varies from the single store owner to large multi state financial institutions with hundreds of branches. Whether you are looking to buy an ATM for your business, start an ATM company of your own, or are looking for ATM service- Best Products is your one stop shop. We are also part of four surcharge free networks, offering traffic driving programs to help you increase foot traffic to your business and increase revenue.
Coin & Currency Counting Equipment
Prior to being a nationwide ATM company, our beginnings in the mid 1970’s were as a Brandt coin & currency counting equipment dealer and service organization. We maintain these roots today as a master dealer  for the most popular brands of money counters such as Billcon, Scan Coin, Glory, and Talaris. Whether you are looking to buy a money counter or bill counter, you count large amounts of change and you need a coin sorter, or you are wrapping large quantities of coin and need a coin wrapper - we have your solution from the top brands.
Self Service Coin
Coin redemption machines are a great way to drive foot traffic to your business. Whether you are a bank or credit union, grocery store or check casher- self service coin redemption is a great way to really cash in. Best Product represents four manufacturers and we have custom solutions tailored to fit your business needs.
Teller Automation
Reallocate human resources, enhance customer services, mitigate risk, and streamline workflow with a teller cash dispenser or teller cash recycler from Best Products. Branch transformation is the latest buzz word in financial branch design and Best Products can guide you all the way with a sales, leasing and service.
Check Automation
Best Products provides check scanning equipment as well as software solutions for your financial institution or business.
New York ATM Services
Our Mission
To be the best. To provide the best equipment, the best service, and the best customer support. We want our customers to know they are getting the best, and should never settle for any less.
History
Having more than 20 years of experience, Chip Botjer and Steve Wilkenshoff established Best Products Sales & Service, Inc. in 1998 to be the premier sales and service provider of money processing equipment, ATM’s, as well as transaction processing services throughout the tri-state area. Best Products Sales & Service, Inc. has grown to be one of the largest and most respected leaders of the industry. After growing too large for our office, we relocated to a larger office and warehouse located right around the corner, still in Floral Park and tripling our space to better serve our customers. Our continued success is built on our promise to provide the very best equipment while supporting all of our products with a full time team of experienced factory trained service technicians. We represent all the major brands including Tranax, Triton, Tidel, Billcon, Scan Coin, Cashscan, DeLaRue, Maverick, Magner, JCM, Rowe, Laurel, Toyocom and many more. Recently, we have added credit card processing also known as merchant services to our long list of services. Whether you’re searching for a new machine, you require service on your old equipment, or you’re simply looking for highly competitive transaction processing; there is only one choice, Best Products Sales & Service, Inc.
Support
Anyone can sell you an ATM or place an ATM Machine in your business, but it's what happens after the sale that matters most and keeping your equipment 100% operational is our #1 priority. Service is what distinguishes Best from the rest... From our own in house full time team of experienced factory trained service technicians, to our friendly and knowledgeable in house customer support staff, only Best Products has the experience and resources to get your machine up and running and keep it that way. Best Products bring new technology and innovation to the forefront with our unique service software platform. This software platform allows us to schedule and prevent service issues before they arise. Our unique software tracks and manages service history, efficiently routes and deploys service technicians, as well as schedules preventative maintenance visits. The software also gives us the ability to compile a detailed service history profile so we can more effectively manage every aspect of your individual ATM or a complete ATM portfolio. Keeping a more traditional approach, we have a full warehouse of in stock parts for all of the machines we sell and our technicians stock the most common parts with them at all times so they have parts readily available to keep you up and running. We take pride in our 4 hour average service call response time. In fact 99% of all service calls are closed the same day they are placed! Our software, experienced personnel coupled with our huge parts arsenal gives us a huge competitive advantage in the industry. Best Products handles all aspects of ATM repair including first line maintenance, second line maintenance, ATM installation, ATM setups, ATM rigging, ATM parts repair, and ATM parts sales. So why settle for anything less than Best?
 







