www.nyandcompany.com

New York & Company offers fashionable women's clothing at a not so glitzy price. Shop for dresses, denim, shorts, skirts, jackets and more. They also have accessories like shoes, jewelry, hats, scarves and more. You can also shop for petite and tall sizes. Exclusively at New York & Company is the Eva Mendes Collection. You can shop her newest collection with items starting at $29. Save on tops, dresses, skirts, pants and jewelry. Eva Mendes also has a Party Collection with dresses for wedding attendees and bridesmaids. Another celebrity is involved with New York & Co and raves about their SOHO jeans. Checkout Jennifer Hudson and all the great looks with the SOHO jeans. The SOHO jean comes in a variety of styles from flare to skinny. The SOHO jean is my favorite! I have so many colors, styles and washes in the legging style. They have the perfect amount of stretch that makes them so comfortable.Have a New York & Company Coupon Code?You can enter the Coupon Code right in your cart in the Coupon Code box. Make sure to hit the Apply button to see the discount come off the items in your cart. Most NY Deals, Clearance and BOGO Sales are excludes from coupons.New York & Co Social Media:FacebookTwitterPinterestGoogle+Instagram Tips & Tricks:New York & Co almost always has a coupon code for you to use on your order. If you don't have a coupon code, you can sign up to the newsletter to get a coupon for $25 off your $75 order. You can also sign up to the newsletter via text. Text WEB to NYSTYL (697895) to subscribe. To opt out you can always text STOP to any message or text STOP to NYSTYL (697895).Want to save even more on top of a coupon? Sign up for the NY&C Rewards credit card. For every $200 you spend on your card you'll get a $10 reward. Plus card holders get special offers like a $10 off birthday coupon, free shipping perks, exclusive cardholder perks and more.Wish List:Create a wish list with New York & Company and you can add items to your list that you want to purchase or have someone purchase for you! You can make the wish list private or public. You can also email it to someone for those not-so-subtle hints! It's easy to add items to your wish list once you are logged in. The button to add items is right next to the 'Add to Bag' button on the product page. Select the color and size of the item you want and click 'Add to Wish List' and you'll see it show up. Need Customer Service?Phone: 1-800-961-9906 Email: service@nyandcompany.com Philanthropy:New York & Company works closely with two foundations, the St. Jude Foundation and the Breast Cancer Research Foundation. Right now you can make a donation to the St. Jude Children's Research Hospital on the NY&C site. You can also support St. Jude's by purchasing a limited edition St. Jude necklace, bracelet or key chain. NY&C will donate 50% from the sale of these items to the St. Jude Children's Research Hospital.Every October, NY&C sells specific items to help raise awareness and find a cure for breast cancer. A portion of the proceeds of these items goes to the Beast Cancer Research Foundation. 

