        9/18/2008
    

Alrighty, I've got some good and bad with this place:Good:- I really like most of their styles, and they have a good range of them too-The prices are affordable and they are always offering specials/sales/and promotions -Their striped collared shirts are my fave...plus they have Tall size pants (and petite)...thank god!!!Not so good:- There's usually no employees located anywhere else in the store other than at the cash register.  If you have questions about merchandise or need a fitting room, take a number and get in line.- While their prices are very affordable, as the saying goes...you get what you pay for.  I don't mean the apparel falls apart or anything, but a lot of the pants wrinkle pretty bad just from sitting down once, and the shirts are the same, even if you heavily starch them




