        11/17/2013
    








4 check-ins
        









            Listed in The Yelp 100 Challenge


I hate malls and I hate shopping for a purpose. But I love shopping online and then returning in stores for free. I love New York and Company for some odd reason, the price and quality is there. They have really great deals if you catch them.This store in NewPark Mall is convenient for me to get to for my returns. One thing about it was when I did my previous return the person at the store asked why I was returning. I said well wrong size. She's like well if you shopped in person, you'd always get the right size. I'm like...right. I just shrugged and went on my merry way.NewPark Mall was my old mall when I grew up. It's pretty much old and run down now, but still is good for its purpose.




