        10/13/2013
    

Here are the reasons why I give this place two stars:Good: 1. Selection of clothing and styles2. Certain outfits better than Express3. High quality material used4. Well-organizedBad: 1. CUSTOMER SERVICE. See what a big difference it makes even though I listed more pros than cons.  The con is bad enough for me to not want to shop at this particular location (atleast).There was only one person working here that did not make me feel uncomfortable. The other two ladies (particularly one of them) looks like she is about to explode any minute out of anger. Meh. That's a big disappointment. I thought it was geared only towards me because one time I came here on a week night to exchange a pair of clothing. However, I went there again today and she was giving the same horrendous attitude to another customer in line. Ridiculous. BEWARE. I don't know her name, and even if i did, I don't intend to exploit an employee. Just making it clear that certain employees need to be swapped if this store at all wants returning customers.




